62
00:04:39,980 --> 00:04:45,120
Some people may distort the /aʊ/ by pronouncing it through their nose.

63
00:04:45,220 --> 00:04:48,980
This happens if you pass the air through your nose too early,

64
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:52,560
before making the /n/ sound.

65
